Class FilteredClassDoc

java.lang.Object
  com.tarsec.javadoc.pdfdoclet.filter.FilteredClassDoc
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.sun.javadoc.ClassDoc, java.lang.Comparable, com.sun.javadoc.Doc, com.sun.javadoc.ProgramElementDoc, com.sun.javadoc.Type
public class FilteredClassDoc
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.sun.javadoc.ClassDoc

Wraps a Javadoc RootDoc object to allow to filter out packages / classes / methods transparently.

$Revision: 1.2 $
